Label: schedule_msg_delete
English: Are you sure you want to delete this event?
Chinese: 您确定要删除这个活动吗？

Label: schedule_msg_two_year
English: You cannot schedule a class beyond two years.
Chinese: 您不能预约两周以后的重复课程。

Label: schedule_msg_overlap
English: You already have a class scheduled during this time. Confirm to schedule?
Chinese: 您在这个时间段已经有课程，确定还要继续排课吗？

Label: schedule_msg_edit_overlap
English: This event has been changed. Please refresh.
Chinese: 当前事件已经被更改，请刷新重试。

Label: schedule_msg_attachment
English: The attachment you uploaded does not meet the requirement.
Chinese: 您上传的附件不符合要求

Label: schedule_schedule_msg_edit_all
English: This is an event in a series. Are you sure you want to edit this and following events?
Chinese: 这是一系列事件中的其中一个，您确定要编辑整个序列吗？

Label: schedule_msg_upload_format
English: Please upload the file in the correct format

Label: schedule_msg_start_current
English: Start time cannot be earlier than current time
Chinese: 开始时间不能早于当前时间

Label: schedule_msg_due_date_earlier
English: The due date cannot be earlier than the scheduled class end time.
Chinese: 截止日期不能早于课程结束事件

Label: schedule_msg_end_time_earlier
English: End time cannot be earlier than start time
Chinese: 结束事件不能早于开始时间
